[[!meta title="Contact"]]

There are many ways to contact us, depending on the subject you want
to talk about.

[[!toc levels=2]]

Public mailing lists
====================

These mailing lists are public and subscription is open to anyone, so avoid
sending sensitive information.

Please respect the [[code of conduct|contribute/working_together/code_of_conduct/]] in all Tails spaces.

<a id="amnesia-news"></a>

amnesia-news
------------

amnesia-news@boum.org is the list where we send our [[news]] by
email. It has a low traffic and is the right place to stay up-to-date with
the releases and security announcements.

<form method="POST" action="https://mailman.boum.org/subscribe/amnesia-news">
	<input class="text" name="email" value=""/>
	<input class="button" type="submit" value="Subscribe"/>
</form>

